create a shared folder with mac & linux

ganis@ganis-ub14-32:~/work$ sudo mkdir /mnt/mac
ganis@ganis-ub14-32:~/work$ sudo chmod 777 /mnt/mac/
ganis@ganis-ub14-32:~/work$ sudo mount -t vboxsf ganis /mnt/mac
ganis@ganis-ub14-32:~/work$ ln -s /mnt/mac/ /home/ganis/mac
ganis@ganis-ub14-32:~/work$ ls /m
media/ mnt/   
 
ganis is the folder name in host
mac is the folder name in guest
